{
  "stem": "27285.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I can't vouch for that if it-- I was told it later or if I remember, so I don't want to go into it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is not truthful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met a few grandmothers, which I didn't know before, but they all died there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they were at-- some at the certain age where it was not so tragic anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was only hard when I came to Palestine later on to tell my father about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For instance, I should tell my father how his mother died.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did she have Typhus, or-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- there was such a lot of sicknesses, and not usual sickness and not like childhood sickness, but like Typhus or-- I don't even know the names anymore.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a sleepness sickness and all this stuff, and tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was-- the whole town was always somehow not clean enough.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The water was not-- was contaminated, so it was very easy not to--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did, but I got over it so it was not so terrible, I guess.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, but I survived it, so I survived Terezin [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I saw a lot of girlfriends die in there also of typhoid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was very hard not to get it, because you were sleeping in such crowded spaces, and there was no-- the sanitary conditions were not of the best.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, it's all a matter of relativity, because later on they were non-existent and you still survived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Cold, influenza, all this-- it's very hard today when you say, ooh, it's freezing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that-- there's no comparison.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you can-- you should never have to go through what you can go through if you have to or want to survive.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
